title: Vote Por Zombozo
description: Cuando el Chatarra debe ponerse a punto en la misma ciudad por donde pasa la campaña de Zombozo, Ben pronto descubre que el payaso usa sus discursos para hipnotizar al pueblo y robarse sus pertenencias. El equipo Tennyson debe impedir que el villano gane las elecciones.

title: Be Afraid of the Dark
description: Ben travels into space to thwart Ghostfreak's diabolical plans. But is he hero enough to take on the Mummy, Werewolf and Frankenstein?

title: Thick as Thieves
description: Phil the Pilferer robs Vambre and Prohyas of their very best Magiswords so he can snag the Sheepy Mantis, but the Warriors find out that no Magisword is lame as they manage to keep Phil from becoming Thief of the Year.

title: Root Beer Guy
description: Root Beer Guy works a boring job during the day and tries to write mystery stories at night. But his life is about to change when he witnesses Finn and Jake kidnapping Princess Bubblegum! There's only one problem: no one believes Root Beer Guy.

title: Terminal Velocity Part 1
description: While Windblade is away on a mission, Bee decides to relive a fun memory.

title: Dia de padres
description: It's Parents' Day at Lakewood Plaza Turbo!
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Bored to Be Wild
description: Mega Man teams up with his crush, Ashley Adderley, to solve a series of science riddles left by Chemical Man, who's plotting to turn all the city's metal into rubber.

title: Telephonies/Tough Love
description: Telephonies: The Gangreen Gang gets hold of the Powerpuff Girls' Hotline and makes crank calls sending the Powerpuff Girls on a wild goose chases all over town./Tough Love: Everyone in Townsville loves the Powerpuff Girls! But the citizens have a sudden change of heart when Him sends out an evil gas turning the entire town against their favorite superheroes.

title: Snots Landing
description: Beth gets Courtney's diorama furniture stuck up her nose and Courtney needs it back before the diorama contest judge arrives.

title: Los Supervillanso se Unen
description: Después de una pausa en las payasadas alienígenas, un inquieto Ben les sugiere a Max y Gwen que podría ser un mejor héroe si fuera solo. Pero cuando Vilgax consigue la ayuda de Zombozo para construir un mecanismo hipnotizador gigante para hipnotizar al mundo entero, Ben debe replantearse su estrategia si quiere derrotar al equipo de supervillanos.

title: Out to Launch
description: While on a visit to Cape Canaveral, the Tennyson Trio are present for the inaugural launch of an experimental space plane. When Vilgax commandeers the ship, Ben must stop the baddie from weaponizing the shuttle before the countdown hits zero.

title: Prankless
description: The guys want to win a prank war with a rival park.

title: Moon Problems
description: The Moon gets sad when Oscar loses his friendship bracelet.

title: Felonious Prose
description: The Warrior mission of finding a lost contact lens gets seriously compromised from Vambre's obsession with the latest Veronica Victorious novel.

title: Past Aliens Present
description: After Ben stumbles upon a video of Cannonbolt ripping up a computer lab on the internet, Team Tennyson must race to State U to find the imposter; but once Ben discovers it is a steam-punk version of his alien that is terrorizing the campus, Ben must take down the man behind the machine, Steam Smythe!

title: Special Delivery
description: Enid and Rad go on a road trip to deliver a package.

title: O Mother, Where Art Thou?
description: Ma Vreedle threatens to blow up the sun if Ben and the Plumbers don't find her missing son!

title: The Powerpuff Girls Best Rainy Day Adventure Ever/Just Desserts
description: The Powerpuff Girls Best Rainy Day Adventure Ever: It's raining in Townsville and there is no crime or villainy afoot. So the girls must stay inside and come up with their very own Powerpuff adventure./Just Desserts: The Smith Family is back and they want revenge. Harold, Maryanne and the kids become a super villain team and make it their goal to destroy the perfect Powerpuff family.

title: El regreso de Xingo
description: Cuando Ben debe divertirse solo durante la merecida siesta de Max, se topa con un juego de Xingo y decide convertirse en OE-Shock Rock para encenderlo. Pero cuando Xingo recibe demasiada carga, salta al mundo real, y nuestro héroe debe quedar frente a frente con su personaje animado favorito.

title: The 11th Alien Part 2
description: After discovering that Vilgax has joined forces with the Weatherheads to trick him into turning over the Omnitrix, Ben must not only overcome his doubts, but fully embrace his new powers if he is to beat his foes.

title: Reststop Roustabout
description: With the Rustbucket stopped on the Midwest roadside, Ben locks himself inside with his tablet as Max and Gwen enjoy the great outdoors, until Team Tennyson is pulled into a wild Jack-a-Lope chase.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Block Party
description: Apple and Onion have to outwit a mean duck who's taken over their building's roof.

title: The Sound and the Furry
description: As Team Tennyson leaves the Frozen Man Festival, Lord Decibel takes center stage to threaten the festival-goers, creating an avalanche if his ransom isn't paid. An over matched Ben must step out of his comfort zone to save the festival from his noisy nemesis!

title: Time Traveling Quick Pants
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn about a quicksand that lets them go back in time.

title: How's This for a Special? Spaaaace
description: After receiving a galactic crime alert the Titans take off for an epic space adventure. The Titans have to stop Darkseid's latest scheme but the excitement of the space adventure might be too much for Robin to handle.

title: Pancake's Bus Tour
description: Apple and Onion go on a guided bus tour as part of their plan to get Apple's shoe back.

title: The Bad Guy Busters
description: Izzy wants to play a superhero game and is willing to do whatever it takes to get the others to see it through.

title: Intravension
description: Los misterios de las Omni-Mejoras se resuelven cuando Ben lucha contra una invasión alienígena proveniente del Omnitrix.

title: La princesa de jade
description: A raíz de un cruel ataque al Palacio, Los Hijos de Garmadon roban la segunda Máscara Oni, y los ninjas invitan a la Princesa Real, Harumi, a su improvisada familia.

title: Lunch with Tabes
description: When Tabes's lunch gets stolen, Tabes launches a full investigation to find the culprit.

title: Ataque en el Palacio de los Panqueques
description: Cuando Gwen se inscribe en un concurso de comer panqueques en el mundialmente famoso Palacio de los Panqueques, Ben encuentra a los Bugg Bros. y debe detenerlos antes de que puedan obtener una provisión infinita del elemento que les da vida a sus creaciones: los panqueques del Palacio del Panqueque.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Memory Part 1
description: Windblade tries to help Bumbleebee but he is wary of this "stranger".

title: Expreso De Gran Estres
description: Durante una transmisión en vivo del nuevo tren bala transcontinental, La Grange se cuela para ganarle al tren. Pero Ben se suma a la diversión, iy no se detendrá ante nada para salir victorioso!

title: Creek Cart Racers
description: A high-speed race with a high-stakes prize may be too much for Craig and his friends.

title: Pantalones Movedizos del Tiempo
description: Oscar y Erizo se enteran de la existencia de unas arenas movedizas que les permiten viajar en el tiempo.

title: Hotdog's Movie Premiere
description: Apple and Onion square off against a no-nonsense security guard after they're banned from the premiere of their friend Hot Dog's new movie.

title: El chillido de hombre muerto
description: La casi desaparición de Zane a manos del Señor "E" obliga a los ninjas a huir a bordo del Bounty, donde descubren que una tramisión que Zane interceptó puede revelar la ubicación oculta del "Silencioso".

title: Summer Love
description: Panda goes on a mission to return a lost phone to the girl of his dreams.

title: Dungeons and Dayjobs
description: A botched mission leaves the Warriors in debt, so they take day jobs at Slugburger and sling Slugburgers for Witchy Simone!

title: Season 3 Recap
description: From the Rubies to the Cluster, catch up on all the highlights from Steven Universe Season 3.

title: Nuggets de Pollo de Sabiduria
description: Cuando Ben y Max comienzan a discutir, Ben se convierte en Fuego para desahogarse, contra la voluntad de Max. Pero una vez que el Dr. Animo lo ve y convierte a Max en un pollo, Ben debe enmendar su error si quiere salvar a su Abuelo y detener al Dr. Animo.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: The 11th Alien Part 1
description: With new Omni-Enhancements in tow, Ben looks to save a town from a sudden mudslide, but his heroics are short lived once Vilgax appears to warn our hero about the consequences of the Omnitrix's mysterious new alien.

title: Monster Visit
description: The monsters get nervous when their Godmonster comes for a visit.

title: Cloris
description: When Clarence befriends an aging woman at the local retirement home, he's determined to remind her of her old self in order to convert the grumpy granny to his fun loving ways.

title: A Fistful of Brains
description: Grandpa Max and Rook are looking all over the galaxy for Ben, who is trapped on Khyber's hidden personal hunting preserve.

title: Buen Viaje
description: Abordo del SS Pettigrew en su último viaje, Ben debe luchar no solo contra el mareo sino también contra Vapor Smythe, que se propone usar a sus criaturas mecánicas para hundir el barco moderno que remplaza al vapor... iy a sus pasajeros!

title: Safari Sa'Bad
description: On their trip to Adrenaworld West, Ben takes a detour on a jungle cruise and finds himself hunted by the evil Tim Buktu. Our hero must outwit the baddie if he wants to make it off the amusement park ride alive!

title: Teletraan X Part 2
description: Investigating a signal in an abandoned missile silo, Bee and Windblade discover their computer back up drone Teletraan X, but it's a trap!

title: La ofensiva de Encantos
description: Cuando Ben recibe demasiada publicidad por sus travesuras alienígenas en Fort Knox, Gwen se pone celosa, se siente poco apreciada, y busca aliviar su dolor con helado. Pero cuando Charmcaster la confronta con la intención de vengar a Michael Morningstar, Gwen debe demostrarse a sí misma que es un miembro digno del equipo Tennyson si quiere sobrevivir.

title: Angel Face
description: BMO ropes his friends into a live action cowboy role-playing adventure!

title: Dr. Animo and the Mutant Ray
description: Dr. Animo has broken out of jail, and has been tracking down Ben, intent on revenge. At the same time, Ben's broken off a piece of the Omnitrix, and as a result, has turned into weird alien combinations, i.e. StinkArms.

title: Red Action to the Future
description: When Red Action is called to the future for an epic battle, Enid is unsure of what to do.

title: Quarantine
description: After a chemical spill, the girls and Mojo find themselves trapped together.

title: Game of Masks
description: As Lloyd and Harumi search the Oni Temple for the last mask, the ninja are taken hostage and discover Princess Harumi's true intentions.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 1
description: With Windblade captured by the Seekers, Bumblebee is on his own for the first time and is responsible for saving Cybertron.

title: Nightmare Hospital
description: Steven and Connie sneak into a hospital to recover Rose's Sword.

title: The Night
description: As night falls in Elmore, the Moon takes us on a tour through the various dreams and nightmares of the town's slumbering inhabitants. Each character's dream shows us their innermost desires, their greatest fears or just how plain weird they are.

title: Innervasion Part 5: High Override
description: While Ben struggles to avoid the High Override's mind control, Max and Gwen enter the Omnitrix to lend a hand, but once they find Ben is not who he seems, Max and Gwen must pull out all the stops if they are to get Ben back in time to save the planet.

title: Paint That a Shame
description: Leshawna creates a paint balloon fight to decide who gets to come with her to an amusement park.

title: Visita Monstruosa
description: Los monstruos se ponen nerviosos cuando su Dios monstruo llega de visita.

title: True Potential
description: Just when the Ninja think they have saved the day, Lord Garmadon returns to Ninjago, and frees Harumi, who encourages him to "achieve his true potential" by conquering the one thing that has always stood in his way, his son, Lloyd.

title: Innervasion Part 3: Strange Bedfellows
description: After the Junkbot shoots the Omnitrix and it begins glowing neon-blue, an imprisoned Vilgax explains it is now a gateway through which the Fulmini Empire will invade Earth, but the only way to stop them is from within the Omnitrix, so Ben must team up with the ultimate baddie if he is to save his planet.

title: La Super Increible Aventura en Balsa
description: Unikitty y Hawkodile están "perdidos en el mar," varados en una balsa juntos. Hawkodile ve esto como una oportunidad para mostrarle a Unikitty que está preparado para cualquier cosa con sus habilidades de experto en supervivencia, pero para su sorpresa, todos sus planes fracasan, mientras que la tonta postura de Unikitty de "todo saldrá bien, vamos a divertirnos" está funcionando de una manera genial. ¿Será Hawkodile capaz de soltar su exceso de preparación para salvarlos a ambos, o acaso la diversión caprichosa de Unikitty será su perdición?

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Burger Run/Monkey See, Monkey Don't
description: Burger Run: When the local Burger Joint is being threatened by a rogue Bakugan, Dan steps up to save the day and the burgers!/Monkey See, Monkey Don't: The AO stop neighborhood kids from copycat behavior (namely, using their Bakugan for frivolous reasons).

title: Despeguemos
description: De excursión en Cabo Cañaveral, el trío Tennyson presencia el lanzamiento inaugural de una nave espacial experimental, pero cuando Vilgax comanda la nave, Ben debe impedir que el villano use el transbordador como arma antes de que la cuenta regresiva llegue a cero.

title: Half-Sies
description: During a trip to the Lake of the Ozarks, Ben and Gwen squabble over Ben's unnecessary "half-birthday" celebration, but when Max gets word of a suspicious rockslide nearby, the cousins must put aside their differences if they are to rescue the trapped miners and uncover who is behind the manmade catastrophe before it's too late: the Bugg Brothers.

title: Bad Bad Cop
description: Vambre and Prohyas pretend to be cops in their attempts to shakedown a dangerous bunch of pirates to find a broccoli smuggler.

title: Double Hex
description: While bird watching at Pinnacles National Park, Gwen and Ben get into a competition of who can spot more birds first, but once a forest fire interrupts their fun, Team Tennyson must hurry if they are to save the bird population and discover who is behind the suspiciously growing fire: Hex!

title: Vote Zombozo!
description: When the Rustbucket must tune-up in the same town as Zombozo's latest campaign trail stop, Ben soon discovers the clown is using his speeches to hypnotize then rob the town, and Team Tennyson must stop the baddie from winning the election.

title: El Onceavo Alienigena Parte 1
description: Con sus nuevas Omni-Mejoras, Ben intenta salvar una ciudad de un repentino alud. Pero su heroísmo dura poco, porque llega Vilgax a advertirlo de las consecuencias del misterioso alien del Omnitrix.

title: Whiteout Part 2
description: Windblade flies to the Himalayas to investigate while Bee watches television, acquiring new verbal "samples".

title: 4 on 1
description: Onion's fear of crowds threatens his basketball team's success.

title: Total Eclipse of the Kart
description: The Powerpuff Girls compete in a race against some of their most vicious villains to win whatever is in the Mayor's mysterious box of mystery.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Steven Universe: Diamond Days Trailer
description: What's waiting for Steven and the gems when they arrive on Homeworld? Get ready for Steven Universe: Diamond Days!

title: Hot Dog estrena su pelicula
description: Cuando unos guardias de seguridad muy serios los echan del estreno de la nueva película de su amigo Hot Dog, Manzana y Cebollín se preparan para pelear.

title: Mayhem in Mascot
description: After their attempt to get a photo with every storefront mascot is foiled, Ben and Gwen sneak out at night to get their photo with the wooden bear totem known as "Yawk", only to find he and the other mascots have come to life!

title: Innervasion Part 4: Mind over Alien Matter
description: While inside the Omnitrix, Ben and Vilgax must work together if they are to close the gateway, but once the Fulmini leader, the High Override, appears, even that might not be enough. Luckily, help arrives in the form of a being calling itself Glitch!

title: Uncle Grandpa Movie
description: The gang attends the premiere of Majestico and Uncle Grandpa Boy, a movie about a little girl who wants to be a super hero.

title: Ben Again and Again
description: After Billy Billions' efforts to carve his face onto Mount Rushmore with a laser are thwarted by Ben, the billionaire brat turns his focus on removing Ben from the Omnitrix, but once he accidentally rips open a rift in space-time, the two must carefully navigate another timeline if they are to return to the present.

title: Ruidosos y Peludos
description: Cuando los Tennyson se van del Festival Frozen Man, Lord Decibel ocupa el escenario central para amenazar a los asistentes y crear una avalancha si no pagan el rescate que pide. iBen se ve superado por su rival y debe salir de su zona de confort para salvar al festival de su entrometido enemigo!

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: All Koiled Up
description: When Ben grows impatient with the snail like pace of gardening, he goes O-E Overflow to pick up the pace and accidentally floods the community garden, but once a giant sink hole appears and frees King Koil and his Kimodo Dragon from below, Ben must quickly right his wrong and capture the baddies if he is to save the coastal city of Bayburgh.

title: Dead Man's Squall
description: Zane's near demise at the hands of Mr. E forces the ninja to flee aboard the Bounty, where they discover that a transmission Zane intercepted may reveal the hidden location of the Quiet One.

title: El sentimiento
description: Mientras Max y Gwen se deleitan en el espíritu navideño de Winter Wonderland, Ben no podría estar más aburrido y concentrado en los juguetes. Pero cuando los Weatherheads fijan sus miras en Winter Wonderland como su próximo objetivo, nuestro héroe debe conectarse con sus emociones si quiere salvar la ciudad.

title: The Fair
description: The Baby Bears make a deal with a carnival worker to be prizes for a game of ball toss.

title: Assault on Pancake Palace
description: When Gwen enters a pancake eating contest at the world famous Pancake Palace, Ben finds the Bugg Bros. and must stop them before they obtain an endless supply of what fuels their creations: Pancake Palace pancakes.

title: Access Denied
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to go to Margaret's birthday party at an exclusive club.

title: El silencioso
description: Mientras que Lloyd y Harumi se aventuran a lo profundo de "Primeval's Eye" en busca de la tercer máscara Oni, los ninja tratan de arreglar al Bounty y hacer un descubrimiento sorprendente.

title: Sabotage Part 2
description: Shockwave creates false memories designed to convince Bee he was always a Decepticon spy.

title: Cone in 60 Seconds
description: After Owen gets ripped off at the ice cream truck, the kids unite to right that wrong.

title: TKO's House
description: TKO is getting restless.

title: Goliad
description: Princess Bubblegum, concerned over her mortality, reveals her designated successor to Finn & Jake - but he still has a lot to learn.

title: Plazaolimpiadas
description: K.O. participa de la competencia anual de Plaza Turbo: los Plazalímpicos.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Enemy of My Enemy
description: When Optimus returns with old friends and dire warnings of a Cybertronian invasion of Earth, the Autobots must split up to defend their old home and their new one, with the Bee Team returning to Cybertron, while Optimus and his All-Stars stay behind to defend against the invasion's advanced force.

title: The Gift
description: The girls must replace the Professor's Christmas present on Christmas Eve.

title: Teletraan X Part 1
description: The Decepticon Armada is nearing Earth to seek the Allspark and are desperate for clues.

title: Dendy's Power
description: Dendy and KO discover a fun and exciting new POW Card exploit.

title: Snake Jaguar
description: In order to join the Sons of Garmadon, Zane (aka Snake Jaguar) participates in a deadly motorcycle initiation race.

title: Mud Is Thicker Than Water
description: Ben, Gwen and Cousin Lucy try to find out how Psyphon's thugs are getting Plumber technology.

title: Ninjago chico, problemas grandes
description: Los ninjas corres a salvar a Lloyd. Un Lord Garmadon más poderoso que nunca, crea una enorme estatua para ayudarlo a gobernar Ninjago y a derrotar a los ninjas.

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: Guar serpiente
description: Para unirse a Los Hijos de Garmadon, Zane (alias Jaguar Serpiente) participa en una carrera de iniciación mortal de motocicletas.

title: The Kid From 3030
description: The kids meet a mysterious kid from the future and try to help him complete his mission.

title: Familiar
description: With many changes going on in his life, Steven tries to find his place in the world.

title: Ye Olde Laser Duel
description: As team Tennyson admires the efficiency of a super modern train station, Ben is quick to sniff out one of Steam Smythe's robots holding up the line. Once the fed up villain tricks our hero into accepting a duel, the fate of the Omnitrix hangs in the balance and it's up to Ben to set things right.

title: Cube Part 2
description: Windblade finds it hard to believe that Bee can't remember his favorite sport, Cube!

title: Popular Banana Split
description: Hedgehog and Max discover a tiny high school when they are accidentally shrunk by a science experiment.

title: Drill of the Hunt
description: Mega Man tries a quick fix using Hypno Woman's powers to rehabilitate Drill Man, to disastrous results!

title: Joshua & Margaret Investigations
description: Finn and Jake's parents hunt an unearthly menace in the woods.

title: The Extinction Event Part 2
description: Shockwave orders the Seekers to help him create an extinction event and destroy all organic life on the planet.

title: Juego de mascaras
description: Mientras Lloyd y Harumi buscan el templo Oni para la última máscara, los ninjas son tomados como rehenes y descubren que verdaderas intensiones de la Princesa Harumi.

title: Animorfosis
description: El trío Tennyson excava fósiles de dinosaurio, pero Ben no sabe que Vilgax y el Dr. Animal se complotaron para robar ADN alien del Omnitrix, pero, una vez extraído el ADN, Vilgax traiciona a su cómplice. Ahora Ben debe aliarse con el malvado doctor si quiere tener la oportunidad de derrotar al gran villano. Pero ¿puede confiar en el Dr. Animal?

title: Ken 10
description: We're back in the future with Ben 10K, and this time he has a son, Ken. On Ken's tenth birthday, Ben gives him his very own Omnitrix. Ben must come to learn to trust Ken with the power of the Omnitrix. Along the way, Ken befriends a kid named Devlin. Devlin turns out to be Kevin 11's son and was merely using Ken so he could break his dad out of the Null Void. Ben 10K and Ken then team up to take down Kevin 11. As for Devlin, he comes to realize his dad is a jerk, and realizes the error of his ways. He's able to redeem himself, proving he's a good kid and joining forces with "Team Tennyson."

title: I.C.E. (In Case of Emergency)
description: When Ice Man decides to be a hero, Mega Man, influenced by Ice Man's literalness, steps down from the hero biz until a true crisis snaps him out of it.

title: Sabotage Part 1
description: From his lab on Cybertron, Shockwave launches an attack on Bee's most vulnerable place...his memories.

title: Fear the Fogg
description: As Max attempts to get Ben and Gwen to the Four Corners Monument before sunset, an ominous fog bank engulfs the roadway and forces Max to drive at a snails pace, but once The Fogg comes to life and attacks the Rust Bucket, Team Tennyson must work together if they are to navigate to safety.

title: Super-Villain Team-Up
description: After a lull in alien antics, a restless Ben suggests to Max and Gwen that he might be a better hero if he went solo, but once Vilgax enlists the help of Zombozo to build a giant hypno-mechanism to hypnotize the entire world, Ben must rethink his strategy if he is to defeat the super-villain team-up.

title: Drone On
description: Ben and Gwen are in a highly competitive paper airplane war, but when alien-tech drones bombard the Rustbucket, the cousins must work together to ground the aerial attack and find out who's behind it: the alien conqueror, Vilgax!

title: The Journey Part 2
description: The Autobots are nearly out of Energon, so they land on a dark planet where they encounter subterranean creatures.

title: An American Benwolf in London
description: Ben and Rook are called to London England to investigate the Forever Knights' latest activities.

title: Siloed Part 1
description: Windblade is playing Cube on Cybertron with Bee when she realizes these are memories and she is still held captive by Slipstream.

title: Cube Part 1
description: Bee discovers a mysterious object in the stolen Decepticon shuttle.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Problemas Lunares
description: La Luna se entristece cuando Oscar pierde su brazalete de la amistad.

title: Brawl Bot
description: Dr. Fox is proud to unveil her new ultimate combat machine and take it into an underground scientist fighting ring. But Hawkodile's jealous of Dr. Fox's fighting bot that's supposedly a better puncher than him and declares he can beat anything it can. To prove his point, he dresses up in spare robot parts and enters himself secretly in the bot battle. With Unikitty as his fighting coach, can Hawkodile survive the tourney, prove he's tougher than a machine, and avoid the scrap yard?

title: Tomemonos un momento
description: El Sr. Gar y Carol se enfrentan a un villano de su pasado.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 1
description: With the help of Teletraan- X, Bee and Windblade excavate an deactivated Autobot that looks like a dinosaur.

title: Bombazobo Vive
description: Durante un viaje de rutina al DMV, Max toma un examen de manejo para renovar su licencia. Pero cuando Zombozo, disfrazado, se apropia del papel del instructor, Ben se convierte en alienígena para detener al malvado y salvar el viaje familiar.

title: Presentando a La Creatura
description: Cuando Max se queda dormido antes de una doble función, Ben y Gwen se ven obligados a salvar el autocine solos. Ocurre que el malvado mago Hex da vida al monstruo de una película, que aterroriza a los espectadores.

title: Steven Universe Season 5 Catch-Up
description: Steven Universe fills you in on everything you need to know about Rose Quartz, the Crystal Gems, and the Diamond Authority before you dive in to new episodes! And there might just be a sneak peek of what's to come.

title: Bee Cool
description: Bee, trying to prove that he can be as cool as Sideswipe and his "intern" Blurr, struggles to lead the Autobots against two Stunticons who stole a trailer full of Cybertronian weapons.

title: Todo Enrollado
description: Cuando Ben se impacienta con el ritmo lento de la jardinería, se convierte en O-E Overflow para acelerar las cosas y, por accidente, inunda el jardín de la comunidad.

title: King Koil
description: Ben and Gwen spend the day volunteering at Repto Ranch and come face to face with King Koil, but need to quickly overcome their fear of snakes if they are to rescue the released critters and defeat the slithery baddie.

title: Bounty Ball
description: While Gwen listens to a lecture on the Transcontinental Railroad, Ben sneaks away to the gift shop. But once the Bounty Hunters appear and corner our hero, Gwen must relay the information she learned on the train and use it to their advantage to help Ben escape.

title: King Gus
description: Things get out of hand when Mr. Gus fulfills a timeless legend and is deemed king of the food court.

title: Xingo's Back
description: Left to entertain himself as Max takes a much deserved nap, Ben stumbles upon a Xingo arcade game and goes OE-Shock Rock to power it up, but when it receives too much juice, Xingo leaps out into the real world and our hero must go toe-to-toe with his favorite cartoon character.

title: The Long Skate Home
description: After they get accused of a crime they didn't commit, the Powerpuff girls and the Derbytantes have to find a way to clear their name!

title: Batalla en El Biggie Box
description: Ben y Billy Billions se enfrentan por un set de sumo exclusivo que se vende únicamente en el centro comercial más grande del mundo, isolo para descubrir que Simon Sez, de apenas seis años, lo compró primero! Así se desata una batalla dentro de una tienda que parece tenerlo todo excepto una salida fácil de encontrar.

title: Jewel of the Aisle/Super Zeroes
description: Jewel of the Isle: A crook hides a huge diamond in a box of the girls' favorite cereal. But how can he trick the girls into giving him some cereal in order to get the jewel back?/Super Zeroes: The girls don't think they have enough superhero accessories like those found in the comic books. They begin to emulate their favorite characters, complete with gadgets and gizmos.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 2
description: Bumblebee doubts his abilities as he has to find the Ark to awaken Optimus and the Autobots.

title: El poder es tuyo
description: Un héroe especial ayuda a Plaza Lakewood Turbo a salvar el planeta.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Beach City Drift
description: Steven and Connie get into a high-speed car race with their biggest foe.

title: Chicken Nuggets of Wisdom
description: When Ben and Max get into an argument, Ben goes Heatblast to blow off steam against Max's wishes; but once Dr. Animo spots him and subsequently turns Max into a chicken, it's up to Ben to right his wrong if he is to save his Grandpa and stop Dr. Animo.

title: Top of the Naughty List
description: It's Christmas Eve and Brock is excited for Santa to come and visit as he settles down for a bedtime story from Master Frown, Unikitty and gang burst in. They are there to stop Master Frown from ruining any more Christmases. Frown pleads innocent but Unikitty and the gang tell the stories of the past Christmases he has already ruined.  Will Frown prove his innocence or will he rocket to the top of the Naughty List?

title: Ben una y otra vez
description: Cuando los esfuerzos de Billy Billiones por tallar su cara en el Monte Rushmore con un láser se ven frustrados por Ben, el malcriado multimillonario se concentra en sacar a Ben del Omnitrix. Pero cuando, por accidente, abre una grieta espacio-temporal, ambos deben navegar con cuidado por otra línea de tiempo si quieren regresar al presente.

title: Frenemies/Strata's Fear
description: Frenemies: Two new Bakugan Brawlers, Shun and Magnus, try out for the AO./Strata's Fear: The AO solve the mystery of a kid's missing Bakugan and meet a Bakugan Hunter named Strata.

title: Tasty Heist
description: Richard's prepared one of the tastiest desserts ever, but he's locked it up tight until the friends have their boring dinner. This will not stand. Unikitty organizes a heist, assembling the friends as a crack team to get in, get out, and eat that tasty snack without Richard knowing. But this heist has hiccups. Can the friends take the cake?

title: Doble Hex
description: Mientras observan aves en el Parque Nacional Pinnacles, Gwen y Ben comienzan a competir para ver quién puede avistar más aves primero. Pero cuando el fuego del bosque interrumpe su diversión, el equipo Tennyson debe darse prisa para salvar a la población de aves y descubrir quién está detrás del fuego que crece sospechosamente: iHex!

title: The Kitty
description: After a mishap in the forest, the Bears lose their own home to dangerous animals.

title: Ballroom
description: MG fixes up the ballroom and warns UG and PS not to step a foot in there until he gets a chance to use it.  But UG mistakenly tosses a ball into the room.  Now PS and UG have to retrieve the ball without touching one foot to the ground.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 1
description: Bee, Windblade and Grimlock finally determine the location of the lost ship, the Ark.

title: Lame Station
description: Pizza Steve tries desperately to make the others in the RV interested in his new game console.

title: Creature Feature
description: When Max dozes off before a double feature, Ben and Gwen are left to save the drive-in by themselves as the evil magician Hex brings the movie monster "That" to life, and unleashes him on the unsuspecting moviegoers.

title: Super Black Friday
description: After being forced to work on a holiday, KO, Rad and Enid take a stand.

title: Atrapagritos
description: Cuando una caries obliga a Ben a ir al dentista, su día empeora aún más cuando el malévolo mago Hex usa un atrapasueños para materializar los miedos de nuestro héroe y los transporta con él a un lugar pesadillesco.

title: El verdadero potencial
description: Justo cuando los ninjas piensan que han salvado el día, Lord Garmadon regresa a Ninjago, y libera a Harumi, quien lo anima a "alcanzar su verdadero potencial" conquistando lo único que siempre se interpuso en su camino, su hijo, Lloyd.

title: King of the Hill Part 1
description: Overconfidence leaves the Bee Team unprepared when they face a Stunticon that can fire guided missiles…on the desert ground above a nuclear waste disposal site!

title: Maccadam's Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bee's memory must be coming back - they access the Hivemind and visit three different eras of Maccadam's.

title: Champions of Breakfast
description: An epic battle between Vambre and her Waffle Magisword and Prohyas' Pancake Magisword escalates to a war that can only end when Grup solicits his Cave Weirdo pals to be peacemakers.

title: Allspark Part 2
description: They search for clues as to the whereabouts of the Allspark and uncover another important memory!

title: Chimney
description: While playing in the woods the boys befriend a wild dog, bring it home and name it Chimney. When the boys find themselves trapped in a well, the new pup is their only hope for escape.

title: Innervasion
description: The mysteries of the Omni-Enhancements are solved when Ben battles an alien invasion coming from inside the Omnitrix.

title: High Stress Express
description: During a live feed of the new transcontinental bullet train, La Grange enters the picture to outrace the train, but Ben joins in on the fun and will stop at nothing to come out on top!

title: La mascara del engano
description: Cuando un sindicato de criminals desconocido amenaza a la Familia Real, los ninjas son llamados de nuevo a la acción y deben proteger a la princesa real y un artefacto legendario que puede tener poderes sobrenaturales.

title: Bon Voyage
description: Aboard the SS Pettigrew on its final voyage, Ben must not only battle seasickness but Steam Smythe, who looks to use his mechanical creatures to sink the steamship's modern replacement and the passengers with it!

title: Big Pup, Little Problem
description: After a mishap in the lab, everyone in the castle- except for Puppycorn- is shrunk to tiny size! Puppycorn thinks it's cool. His friends are like living action figures! So he begins playing with them in imaginary adventures. Unikitty and the others think being miniature and playing with Puppycorn is surprisingly fun, but PC has a habit of accidentally breaking his toys, and it's soon clear the gang will have to make a daring, tiny escape back to the lab before Puppycorn loves them to pieces!

title: Bomzobo Lives
description: During a routine trip to the DMV, Max takes a driving test to renew his license, but when a disguised Zombozo hijacks the role of instructor, Ben goes alien to stop the baddie and save their family road trip.

title: Es mi Fiesta
description: Oscar y Erizo planean una fiesta de cumpleaños sorpresa para Susie.

title: Ragnarock and Roll
description: When an ancient prophecy spells doom for Townsville, the girls must race to stop it.

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 2
description: Teletraan-X's scans reveal their old friend Grimlock, who is intent on finding the rest of his missing dinosaur friends.

title: Fractured Part 1
description: Windblade discovers Bumblebee in the desert on his own.

title: The Climb
description: Craig's phone gets stuck in Mt. Sycamore, the tallest tree in the creek!

title: 4 a 1
description: El temor de Cebollín a las multitudes amenaza el éxito de su equipo de baloncesto.

title: Legs from Here to Homeworld
description: Steven travels to visit family.

title: Season 4 Recap
description: Catch up with this Steven Universe Season 4 recap.

title: La noche de los villanos en casa
description: Mientras Box-man y Venomous no están, Darrell y Shannon cuidan a Fink, aunque él no quiera.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: The Jade Princess
description: In the wake of a vicious attack upon the palace, the Sons of Garmadon steal the second Oni Mask, and the ninja invite the royal princess, Harumi, into their makeshift family.

title: Save Mojo/Substitute Creature
description: Save Mojo: An animal activist group sets out to protect Mojo, ensuring that he can behave like the naturally evil monkey that he is./Substitute Creature: A substitute teacher comes to Pokey Oaks and the girls are sure that this creature teacher is up to no good.

title: Tiempo de Sonar
description: Después de una serie de pesadillas recurrentes que afectan su sueño, Ben se niega a contarles a Max y Gwen lo que le molesta. Pero una vez que se dan cuenta de que el propio Zombozo está detrás de las pesadillas, Ben debe aceptar la ayuda de Max y Gwen si quieren ponerle fin al terror.

title: Evil's Encore
description: Dr. Animo reminisces about when he once took control of the Plumber's HQ in Mount Rushmore. (Flashback episode.)

title: The Quiet One
description: As Lloyd and Harumi venture deep into Primeval's Eye in search of the third Oni Mask, the ninja attempt to fix the Bounty and make a startling discovery.

title: A Media
description: Durante un viaje al Lago de los Ozarks, Ben y Gwen discuten sobre la innecesaria celebración de "medio cumpleaños" de Ben. Pero cuando Max se entera de un sospechoso desprendimiento de rocas cercano, los primos deben dejar de lado sus diferencias si quieren rescatar a los mineros atrapados y revelar quién está detrás de la catástrofe producida por el hombre antes de que sea demasiado tarde: los hermanos Bugg.

title: Christmas Movies
description: On Christmas Eve, the Baby Bears defend a video store from getting robbed.

title: King of the Hill Part 2
description: The harried Autobots' Stunticon enemy proves more formidable and crafty than they anticipated, using his guided missiles to threaten a nuclear waste disposal site.

title: Desastre en Mascota
description: Frustrado su intento de conseguir una foto con cada mascota de vidriera, Ben y Gwen se escabullen de noche para tomarse su foto con el tótem del oso de madera... iy descubren que él y las demás mascotas cobraron vida!

title: Atrapa la Botella
description: Manzana y Cebollín inventan un nuevo juego que atrae una atención inesperada.

title: Atrapa la Botella
description: Manzana y Cebollín inventan un nuevo juego que atrae una atención inesperada.

title: Siloed Part 2
description: Windblade manages to fight her way out when Slipstream is called away and she discovers Bee and Teletraan-X are there to help!

title: Enter the Wood Man
description: Mega Man accidentally awakens Wood Man, who thinks it's still the Hard Age, sets off on a path of destruction toward Silicon City.

title: Fiesta en la Cuadra
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben ser más astutos que un pato malvado que se apoderó del techo de su edificio.

title: Fiesta en la Cuadra
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben ser más astutos que un pato malvado que se apoderó del techo de su edificio.

title: Trust Your Guts, Man!
description: Guts Man tries to undo Dr. Light's eco-friendly disposal of trash in Silicon City by infiltrating the family and destroying the Lighthouse so he can eat it!

title: The Loophole
description: Gumball and Darwin give Bobert specific instructions to ensure he acts in a safe and responsible manner. When Bobert starts applying his robot logic to their rules, they soon realize they're going to have to be much clearer. Or he will end up destroying them all.

title: Screamcatcher
description: When a cavity forces Ben to the dentist his day gets even worse when the malevolent magician Hex uses a nearby dream catcher to bring our hero's fears to life and transports them both to a nightmarish dreamscape.

title: Alienigenas del Pasado, Presente
description: Cuando Ben encuentra un video en Internet en el que Cannonbolt destruye un laboratorio informático, el equipo Tennyson debe correr a State U para encontrar al impostor. Pero una vez que Ben descubra que una versión a vapor de su alienígena es la que está aterrorizando al campus, deberá derribar al hombre que está detrás de la máquina: iVapor Smythe!

title: Beach Daze
description: Unikitty and the gang gear up for a fun day at the beach... but when Master Frown shows up as the lifeguard to spoil their plans in the sand, Unikitty and the gang embark on a beach quest to find the legendary Perfect Spot, far away from Frown's tyrannical rule. But can they get there before Frown and claim it for their own or will their quest turn out to be a real beach bummer?

title: Thanksgiving
description: When Raven's father Trigon shows up for Thanksgiving dinner, Robin's seating plan isn't the only thing that gets ruined.

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 2
description: Bee remembers an early version of Megatron where he was a gladiatorial hero, but realizes how dangerous he became.

title: That's the Stuff
description: While touring a space museum, Ben's excitement multiplies when he learns that recently discovered space stuff is being examined inside the museum's lab. Once the stuff comes to life and the shape-shifting goo replicates our hero, Ben must look within if he is to stop the case of mistaken identity.

title: Space Mission: Danger
description: After their spaceship explodes, Unikitty and the gang float helplessly through space. As they try to formulate a plan that will get them home safe, they flash back to how each of them is responsible for their ship being destroyed. Will they make it home, and more importantly who will be to blame if they don't.

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 1
description: Windblade explains the threat of Megatron and the Decepticons to Bee.

title: Innervasion Part 2: Call the Dream Police
description: After defeating the Warbot and discovering Vilgax inside, Ben's "secret voices" only worsen and begin affecting his sleep, but once Gwen discovers a sleepwalking Ben using missing items from the campsite to create his own massive Junkbot, it is up to Ben to stop his own creation.

title: The Interrogation
description: After Mr. Reese discovers his precious car smeared with meatball sauce, he pulls out his officer's cap and enlists Clarence to help his investigation to nab the culprit.

title: Los Safaris son Malos
description: En su paseo a Adrenaworld West, Ben toma un desvío por una selva y descubre que lo persigue el malvado Tim Buktu. iNuestro héroe debe ser más listo que el villano si quiere llegar al parque de diversiones con vida!

title: How's This for a Special? Spaaaace Part 1
description: After receiving a galactic crime alert, the Titans take off for an epic space adventure.

title: Can I Keep It?
description: After stumbling upon a cute cat-dog-rabbit creature hybrid, or "Cadobbit," Ben ignores Grandpa Max's advice and sneaks the animal onto the Rustbucket, but is quickly in over his head as Dr. Amino's creation turns on him!

title: Eruption Part 1
description: As the Autobots discover the Ark, they have to wake up their friends in this battle for the future.

title: Vuela Dron
description: Ben y Gwen se enfrentan en una guerra de avioncitos de papel sumamente competitiva. Pero cuando unos drones con tecnología alienígena bombardean el Rustbucket, los primos deben trabajar juntos para derribar el ataque aéreo y descubrir quién está detrás de eso: iVilgax, el conquistador extraterrestre!

title: Local Heroes/Pegatrix
description: Local Heroes: After the AO cause accidental destruction Dan's parents question whether the kids should be allowed to keep their Bakugan./Pegatrix: Lia disagrees with her new Bakugan Pegatrix on battle techniques but during a fierce fight Lia must rely on Pegatrix's battle savy.

title: Freezer Burn
description: Batman and Firestorm team up to fight their respective cold villains, Mr. Freeze and Killer Frost. Complications arise when Firestorm's infatuation for the wily Ms. Frost gets the best of him.

title: El Antiguo Duelo Laser
description: Mientras el equipo Tennyson admira la eficiencia de una estación de tren súper moderna, Ben olfatea rápidamente a uno de los robots de Vapor Smythe, que está demorándose más de la cuenta. Pero cuando el villano, harto de esperar, engaña a nuestro héroe para que acepte un duelo, el destino del Omnitrix está en la cuerda floja y Ben es el encargado de arreglar las cosas.

title: Power Punchers
description: Fed up with losing in video games to his Dad, Craig seeks training in the Creek.

title: Him Diddle Riddle
description: The Powerpuff Girls must solve a series of Him's riddles to keep the Professor from having to pay.

title: Under a Red Sun
description: Steppenwolf "boom tubes" Superman to a planet with a red sun in order to make the Man of Steel powerless. Somehow Batman and Big Barda have to locate the planet before Superman is destroyed.

title: The Journey Part 1
description: Bee accesses a memory from onboard the Ark on its journey from Cybertron to Earth.

title: Trucker Hall of Fame
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to help Muscle Man get to the Big Rig Museum to spread his dad's hat's ashes.

title: Blurred
description: After his reckless actions cause the escape of a dangerous Sharkticon weapons engineer, Sideswipe goes out of his way to recapture the 'Con and prove his value to the Team in fear of getting replaced by a younger, and faster, newcomer -­‐‑Rescue Bot Blurr!

title: Bottle Catch
description: Apple and Onion's favorite game attracts some unexpected attention.

title: Shadowstriker Part 1
description: Bee doubts his fighting abilities as he continually loses in practice to Windblade.

title: Animorphosis
description: As the Tennyson trio dig up dinosaur fossils in the Badlands, Ben is unaware that Vilgax and Dr. Amino have teamed up to steal alien DNA from within the Omnitrix, but once extracted, Vilgax double crosses his fellow villain. Ben must now join forces with the evil doctor to have a chance to defeat the big baddie, but can Dr. Amino be trusted?

title: Season 2 Recap
description: Catch up with this Steven Universe Season 2 recap.

title: It's My Party
description: Oscar and Hedgehog plan a surprise birthday party for Susie.

title: Whiteout Part 1
description: Bee remembers his escape pod from the Ark crashed in the snowy Himalayas.

title: Cazarecompensas
description: Mientras Gwen escucha una conferencia sobre el Ferrocarril Transcontinental, Ben se escapa en secreto a la tienda de regalos. Pero una vez que los Cazarrecompensas aparecen y acorralan a nuestro héroe, Gwen debe transmitir la información que aprendió en el tren y utilizarla para ayudar a Ben a escapar.

title: Space Oddity
description: In the year 3021, the gang's intergalactic mission goes awry when a strange alien creature infiltrates their ship.

title: Diary
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to fix a lock on Margaret's diary before she gets back from a weekend trip.

title: Allspark Part 1
description: Hiding from the Decepticons, Windblade use her Cityspeaker powers to search Bee's memory files.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Galactic Wonder
description: Wonder Woman has won student of the month at Super Hero High again!  As a special surprise Principal Waller has flown in Wonder Woman's mother, Queen Hippolyta, for a visit. Queen Hippolyta is not happy with what she finds and demands that Wonder Woman return to school at the island paradise of Themyscira. Hoping to take her mind off of her troubles with her mother Wonder Woman, Batgirl and Supergirl decide to investigate a strange electromagnetic anomaly. Their investigation leads them to the hideout of Lena Luthor where they discover a plot between her and Eclipso to transform the planet Earth into a new version of Gemworld!  The girls will have to split up to find the generators scattered around the planet and destroy them. They'll also have to overcome Lena's new breed of mood altering Kryptomites to save the day and convince Queen Hippolyta that Super Hero High is the best school for Wonder Woman!

title: Puddle Eyes
description: A nap in mud seals Clarence's eyes and leaves him sightless, potentially dooming his team's chances in the school's ill-conceived "Vision Bee."

title: The Charm Offensive
description: After Ben gets too much publicity for his alien antics in Fort Knox, a jealous Gwen feels unappreciated and looks to ease her pain with ice cream, but once she is confronted by Charmcaster looking to avenge Michael Morningstar, Gwen must prove to herself she's a worthy member of Team Tennyson if they are to survive.

title: Dreamtime
description: After a series of reoccurring nightmares affect his sleep, Ben refuses to open up to Max and Gwen about what's bothering him, but once they realize Zombozo himself is behind it, Ben must accept Max and Gwen's help if they are going to put a stop to the terror.

title: El Popular Banana Split
description: Erizo y Max descubren una escuela diminuta cuando, por accidente, un experimento científico los encoge.

title: Power Cycle
description: After replicating Elec Man's powers, an underslept/overcharged Mega Man goes on a 24/7 hero spree that ends up turning him into his own worst enemy.

title: Teman a la Niebla
description: Mientras Max intenta llevar a Ben y Gwen al Monumento de las Cuatro Esquinas antes del atardecer, un banco de niebla siniestra envuelve la carretera y obliga a Max a conducir a la velocidad de un caracol. Pero una vez que Fogg cobra vida y ataca el Rust Bucket, el equipo Tennyson debe trabajar unido si se quieren llegar sanos y salvos.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Eruption Part 2
description: Teletraan-X has to reboot the offline computer systems to wake up their Autobot friends and the ship while fighting the Deceptions.

title: The Feels
description: While Max and Gwen revel in the holiday spirit of Winter Wonderland, Ben couldn't be more unamused and focused on the toys, but once the Weatherheads set their sights on Winter Wonderland as their next target, our hero must become one with his emotion if he is to save the town.

title: Origin of Species
description: Origin of Species, Part 1: Dan meets his partner Bakugan Drago for the first time and we learn about the incident that happened on Earth twelve years ago./Origin of Species, Part 2: Dan and friends win the Bakugan Battle, firmly establishing the Awesome Ones as our heroes and Bakugan Brawlers.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Big Trouble, Little NinjaGo
description: The ninja race to save Lloyd, as a more powerful-than-ever Lord Garmadon creates an enormous Colossi to help him rule Ninjago and defeat the ninja.

title: The Question
description: Gumball and Darwin seek the answer to the biggest question of all: what is the meaning of life? They need to understand the point of their lives, so resolve to seek advice from everyone in Elmore. They ask people, animals and even planets but their answer comes from an unexpected source.

title: The Mask of Deception
description: When an unknown criminal syndicate threatens the Royal Family, the Ninja are called back into action and must protect the royal princess and a fabled artifact that may hold supernatural powers.

title: Season 1 Recap
description: Catch up with this Steven Universe Season 1 recap.

title: Battle at Biggie Box
description: Ben and Billy Billions go head to head over a Sumo Slammer Set sold exclusively inside the world's largest shopping center, only to find six-year-old Simon Sez has gotten it first! A battle royal ensues inside a store that seemingly has everything except an easy to find exit.

title: Monster Chef
description: Axl and Chef Éclair must enter a cooking contest to try to keep Jestro from getting the hottest chili recipe in the realm.

title: Shadowstriker Part 2
description: Through memory, Bee is shown some of his past triumphs, like rescuing Optimus from Shadowstriker.

title: The Extinction Event Part 1
description: Decepticons Shockwave and Shadowstriker arrive on Earth with a simple plan to find the Allspark.

title: Sabro Atraco
description: Richard preparó uno de los postres más sabrosos de todos los tiempos, pero lo cerró con llave hasta que los amigos terminen su cena aburrida. Esto no va a seguir así. Para organizar un atraco, Unikitty organiza a sus amigos como un comité de expertos para entrar, salir y comer ese sabroso bocadillo sin que Richard lo sepa. Pero este atraco tiene un traspié. ¿Podrán los amigos llevarse el pastel?

title: Puedo Quedarmelo?
description: Tras toparse con una adorable criatura, híbrido de gato, perro y conejo, Ben no hace caso al consejo del abuelo Max y se lleva al animal a escondidas al Chatarra. Pero pronto empiezan los problemas porque ila creación del Dr. Animal lo delata!

title: Lost Playground
description: When Aberdale Elementary's beloved playground equipment is replaced with safe, boring alternatives, Clarence and the gang seek out their old playground equipment in the legendary lost playground yard.

title: That's a Wrap
description: Duncan goes on a mission to scare Courtney during a field trip to the museum.

title: Busted Cart
description: Mordecai and Rigby bust up the cart while doing stunts and have to figure out a way to fix it.

title: The Good Lars
description: Steven, Lars and Sadie get invited to a party with the Cool Kids.

title: Big Pinchy
description: JP leads his friends on a voyage to find the biggest crayfish in the creek.

title: How's This for a Special? Spaaaace Part 2
description: The Titans have to stop Darkseid's latest scheme, but the excitement of the space adventure might be too much for Robin to handle.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 2
description: Slipstream and her Seekers engage in battle as our heroes trek towards the Ark.

title: The Car
description: Gumball and Darwin accidentally destroy Mr Robinson's new car...or do they?

title: Terminal Velocity Part 2
description: Bee finds himself on Velocitron with Hod Rod to have some fun but it turns into a nightmare as the Plague of Rust descends.

title: Rey Koil
description: Ben y Gwen pasan el día como voluntarios en Repto Ranch y se enfrentan cara a cara con el Rey Koil. Pero necesitan superar rápidamente su miedo a las serpientes si quieren rescatar a las criaturas liberadas y derrotar al serpenteante villano.

title: Dread on Arrival
description: The ninja appeal to the police commissioner of Ninjago in an effort to help save Lloyd and thwart Harumi's efforts to resurrect the evil Lord Garmadon.

title: El Paseo en Autobus de Pancake
description: Manzana y Cebollín suben a un autobús que da un tour guiado como parte de su plan para recuperar el zapato de Manzana.

title: El Paseo en Autobus de Pancake
description: Manzana y Cebollín suben a un autobús que da un tour guiado como parte de su plan para recuperar el zapato de Manzana.

title: Maccadam's Part 1
description: Bee and Windblade avoid an attack by Slipstream and Bee asks to go to Maccadam's!

title: Innervasion Part 1: Message in a Boxcar
description: As Team Tennyson prepares their boxcar for an upcoming race, Ben is hearing voices and is unable to go Upgrade to enhance his car, but once the race is interrupted by a mysterious Warbot, Ben must overcome the voices inside his head if he is to defeat the giant adversary.

title: La Naturaleza de las Cosas
description: Mientras pasean por el Parque Nacional Geyser Gulch, el trío Tennyson descubre un generador a vapor de Steam Smyth y debe apagarlo antes de que sobrecargue la red eléctrica o, peor, icause un terremoto masivo que destruya el parque entero!

title: Es la cosa
description: Mientras visita un museo espacial, la emoción de Ben se multiplica cuando se entera de que están examinando en el laboratorio unas "cosas espaciales" que acaban de descubrir. Pero cuando esa cosa viscosa cobra vida y comienza a replicar a nuestro héroe con su capacidad de cambiar de forma, Ben debe buscar en su interior si quiere detener el caso de identidad equivocada.

title: The New Frontier
description: When Jake has a dream that predicts when his last days are, Finn intervenes when the events of the dream start to actually happen.

title: Parada de Descanso
description: Con el Rustbucket detenido en la carretera del Medio Oeste, Ben se encierra con su tablet mientras que Max y Gwen disfrutan del hermoso paisaje, hasta que el equipo Tennyson debe involucrarse en una persecución salvaje de un jackalope.

title: Fractured Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bumblebee does not remember her and her mission to find the Allspark is critical.

title: The Oni & the Dragon
description: While Princess Harumi adjusts to life with the ninja, Lloyd and Jay search for answers about the Oni Masks, while Cole and Zane attempt to infiltrate the Sons of Garmadon.

title: Terror llegando
description: Los ninjas recurren al comisionado de la policía de Ninjago en un esfuerzo por ayudar a salvar a Lloyd y frustrar los esfuerzos de Harumi de resucitar al malvado Lord Garmadon.

title: Memory Part 2
description: Windlbade and Bumblebee are attacked by Decepticons and she regains his trust.

title: Bully for You/Trolling for Laughs
description: Bully for You: The AO must handle a neighborhood bully who is using his Bakugan to pick on the local kids./Trolling for Laughs: Wynton's constant practical jokes wear thin on his Bakugan Trox so the Bakugan decide to teach him a lesson.

title: El oni y el dragon
description: Mientras que la Princesa Harumi se adapta a la vida con los ninjas, Lloyd y Jay buscan respuestas sobre las máscaras Oni, mientras que Cole y Zane intentan infiltrarse en Los Hijos de Garmadon.

title: Hat Trick
description: When Felix Faust steals Zatanna's magical top hat, the Justice League must help retrieve it before the evil wizard can use it to create a magic portal, releasing the demon Ghast.

title: The Nature of Things
description: While sightseeing at the Geyser Gulch National Park, the Tennyson trio uncover Steam Smythe's steam-powered generator and must shut it down before it overloads the power grid or, even worse, causes a massive earthquake that destroys the entire park!
